{"tid":1437378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譴責美國背後操作香港反送中 《央視》：立秋了，秋後該辦啥事呢？","createTime":"2019-08-09T13:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T19:38:01.000Z","uid":37757,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf95b3bad03fa5c34ca275356e63bdb6a51e351","tid":1437378,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"香港反送中抗議持續在各地進行，香港政府與中國政府多次發出嚴厲譴責與警告，官媒也透過評論或節目強調中國政府有能力解決「暴徒」引起的「動亂」。<br />\n<br />\n中國媒體《央視》的節目《主播說聯播》中，主播郭志堅8日說到，「今天立秋，到了秋天後該辦啥事呢？」暗指香港接下來可能會出現「秋後算帳」的情況。<br />\n<br />\n該主播暗指香港抗議人士可能會被秋後算帳。（湯森路透）<br />\n<br />\n根據報導，郭志堅直指香港「港獨」組織負責人美國領事館的官員在飯店裡會面，「亂港幕後黑手已經明目張膽從幕後走向台前，外交部駐港公署緊急向美方提出交涉。」<br />\n<br />\n郭志堅也提到，「香港暴力事件」是美國的「作品」，指責美國「赤裸裸干涉別國內政真的是很沒品」，甚至應該將此行為稱為「作惡」。最後，郭志堅說，「伸手必被捉。香港不會也不允許這麼無休止地亂下去。今天立秋，到了秋天後該辦啥事呢？想想看吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiokKv6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiokKv6.gif&h=b05ab9a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f10c04751c748e94be5073d42838e5c336afaf1","tid":1437378,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fac971b22bccff68cd976c71a4e9ec38e974e8","tid":1437378,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dbe3fcb268e4828cf16088b41fb679524ecbc4","tid":1437378,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">下流賤格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一味靠嚇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</span></div></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d33c522bb6c43840dbaa2b268b2d828a12a901fe","tid":1437378,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0007f9fdb93e5e225b2a1e4a134f048e8fc8796","tid":1437378,"uid":46966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉鳩黃之峰啦正仆街黎 搞港獨<br />\n我地愛國愛港 擁護一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8bf52ebcc2e6ac6c68c8f345f714cd83652931","tid":1437378,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0007f9fdb93e5e225b2a1e4a134f048e8fc8796","tid":1437378,"uid":46966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉鳩黃之峰啦正仆街黎 搞港獨<br />\n我地愛國愛港 擁護一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"愛国之友連登 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61be5ec166ae9310d49ec334f8045352ac54d751","tid":1437378,"uid":275175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"無錯, 一定要同林奠算帳, 咪能比條賤種側側膊"},{"pid":"209ea53ab6c2d1dca66bcbb2044df82a80b74881","tid":1437378,"uid":294646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbf95b3bad03fa5c34ca275356e63bdb6a51e351","tid":1437378,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"香港反送中抗議持續在各地進行，香港政府與中國政